  "slug": "invview",
  "title": "Inv View",
  "description": "Allows you to open and manipulate the inventories and ender chests of online and offline players. Server Side",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\"><strong><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CottonMC/Vivatech/master/docs/fabric_badge.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"77\" /></strong></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Fabric Server-Side&nbsp;</strong>mod.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Allows you to open and manipulate the inventories and ender chests of online and offline players.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Only needs to be installed on the server!</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Supports trinkets</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Supports LuckPerms</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Inventory</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/elpDEle.gif\" alt=\"Manipulate Inventory Gif\" width=\"524\" height=\"230\" /></span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Ender Chest</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dqVrUmX.gif\" alt=\"Manipulate Ender Chest Gif\" width=\"524\" height=\"210\" /></span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Offline Players</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dhQ7czc.gif\" alt=\"Manipulate Offline Gif\" width=\"524\" height=\"189\" /></span></p>\n<h3><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Command</span></strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">/view (inv<strong>|</strong>echest) &lt;playername&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">(Requires OP)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Permissions</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">invview.command.root - allows player to use /view</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">invview.command.inv- allows player to use /view inv</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">invview.command.echest- allows player to use /view echest</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">invview.command.trinket- allows player to use /view trinket</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">invview.protected- protects player's inventories from being opened</span></p>\n<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">invview.can_modify- prevents players from editing viewed inventories (defaults to true)</span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
